item.title: Amazing Youtube Artists
item.description: Great music is not always endorsed by deep pockets. The Youtube platform has allowed some of the best moments in music to be captured and shared. There are several artists that are either earning noteriety or gaining it, not because some hot-shot on Music Row decided it, but because we-the-people loved them. Here are some of my favorites. Chelsea Constable I’m putting Chelsea and Grace at the top of the list because they illustrate what my post is all about.
